{"tid":617456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工程師：條鐵出事即條軌出事囉","createTime":"2018-04-05T03:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T10:28:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f4a3a36276f67425533a9c4f12e104f9ec8cf2","tid":617456,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:42:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352502&d=zc069oswvsp2mKSTV1okG2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3861c35d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352502&h=d97d42b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352502</a><br />\n<br />\n工程師：條鐵出事即條軌出事囉<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180405/large/05la1p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180405%2Flarge%2F05la1p02.jpg&h=512df3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工程人員沿路檢視涉事路軌。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵昨強調事故不涉列車及路軌問題，車務營運總管李聖基亦解釋是承托軌道的工字鐵輕微變形。但公共專業聯盟政策召集人黎廣德批評港鐵的說法取巧，擔心港鐵忽視真正問題所在，「承托路軌嘅工字鐵出事，咁咪即係條路軌出事囉」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倡機電工程署介入調查<br />\n<br />\n本身是資深工程師的黎廣德認為，港鐵由昨凌晨發稿公佈事件，至黃昏開記者會解畫，前後只有短短約16小時，但港鐵已立即排除列車出現問題的可能性，是非常不嚴謹的說法，「雖然佢話之後會繼續調查，但如果已經講明唔關列車事，將調查方向收窄至工字鐵上，咁可能會忽視咗其他問題」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指即使相信列車一切正常，但路軌問題仍反映工程的設計或施工失當，因工字鐵變形並非不可預見的情況，理應在設計初期已考慮，無理由在通車前數個月才發現，港鐵有必要承擔責任。他指事件涉公眾安全，機電工程署應引用法定權力主動到場調查，不可只依賴港鐵提交報告，否則會嚴重影響公眾對高鐵安全的信心。<br />\n<br />\n鐵路專業人員工會主席林偉強則指，列車出軌非常罕見，過往很少聽聞，但按照港鐵對事故的描述，相信只是小問題，不會導致列車飛脫。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳建平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t隧道漏水　組件破損　工程安全成疑<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t【蘋果照相機】出軌？冇問題！<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t高鐵試車　3日出軌承托路軌工字鐵變形　叫停測試<br />\n頭條 5小時前"},{"pid":"4439ead68e5cb0db8eefe228ccac4256741c5d4f","tid":617456,"uid":83648,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"一個港豬澳一個鳩鐵"},{"pid":"34d38392fb6ddc06be27b030eda5e48b21301df6","tid":617456,"uid":35430,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"華人當家作主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賤種基因畀返英國佬管啦"},{"pid":"484249610e04e37995cfa6fcdfc0065bafa4155f","tid":617456,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4ca5b0282fe02a7cfe46c26ab29d8a8d442c7b","tid":617456,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"做得老母一定係女人"},{"pid":"582b96b329a1f8f2ee8dcf71f4cb46353de3a1b9","tid":617456,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9917f412fab4664e68e8c8c7f8a56ad76a97dc3","tid":617456,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5178f199490af92af8ae2624d07fae2670ee77","tid":617456,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4439ead68e5cb0db8eefe228ccac4256741c5d4f","tid":617456,"uid":83648,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"一個港豬澳一個鳩鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:19:30.000Z","msg":"好難估邊一邊會出事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69606a27a1415abb0a326b6908562df88eaf318","tid":617456,"uid":155818,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"6b5178f199490af92af8ae2624d07fae2670ee77","tid":617456,"uid"